Day 58 — Road to Fluent Spanish Summary
Day 58 focused on new Puerto Rico travel conversation phrases, practical restaurant Spanish, weather/taxi vocabulary, music/concert phrases, and continued review of Pimsleur Unit 2 Lesson 14.

Duolingo Review
Reviewed several travel and everyday phrases including:

El bar está enfrente del cine = The bar is across from the movie theater
El mismo autobús = The same bus
Todavía no entiendo = I still don’t understand
Hacen ejercicio = They exercise
Se quedan allí = They stay there
Hasta muy tarde = Until very late
Ahí viene el profe = There comes the teacher
Esta clase me duerme = This class puts me to sleep
Weekly Conversational Phrases
Started the new weekly phrase set focused on restaurants, Puerto Rico travel, and natural conversation:

¿Qué me sugieres pedir? = What do you suggest I order?
¿Cuál es tu comida favorita de aquí? = What’s your favorite food from here?
Quisiera algo típico de Puerto Rico = I would like something typical from Puerto Rico
¿Qué lugares recomiendas para salir? = What places do you recommend for going out?
Es mi primera vez aquí = It’s my first time here
Todavía estoy aprendiendo español = I’m still learning Spanish
Perdón, estoy un poco confundido = Sorry, I’m a little confused
¿Puedes repetir eso, por favor? = Can you repeat that, please?
La comida estuvo muy buena = The food was very good
Definitivamente quiero regresar = I definitely want to come back
